premise_source_doc_sentence: The film saw the highest number of ticket sales in the US ever for a romantic comedy , with Box Office Mojo listing it as the # 1 romantic comedy by the highest estimated domestic tickets sold at 42,176,400 , slightly ahead of My Big Fat Greek Wedding  (  2002  )  at 41,419,500 tickets .

Between 1960 and 1964 , 22 of his songs placed on the Billboard Top 40 , including `` Only the Lonely ''  (  1960  )  , `` Crying ''  (  1961  )  , and `` Oh , Pretty Woman ''  (  1964  )  .

Orbison posthumously won the 1991 Grammy Award for Best Male Pop Vocal Performance for his live recording of `` Pretty Woman '' on his HBO television special Roy Orbison and Friends , A Black and White Night .
